definitions.definition: An English surname , thought to be habitational .
James Garfield , the 20th President of the United States .
A male given name transferred from the surname .

subdefinitions.definition: A former rural locality in Barcaldine Region, central Queensland , Australia .
A town in the Shire of Cardinia , Victoria , Australia , south-east of Melbourne .
A community in Mountain View County , Alberta , Canada , named after US president James A. Garfield .

A number of places in the United States : A town in Benton County , Arkansas . A census-designated place in Chaffee County , Colorado . A minor city in Emanuel County , Georgia . An unincorporated community in Bonner County , Idaho . An unincorporated community in Bonneville County and Jefferson County , Idaho , named after the US president. An unincorporated community in Osage Township, LaSalle County , Illinois . An unincorporated community in Union Township, Montgomery County , Indiana . A minor city in Pawnee County , Kansas . An unincorporated community in Breckinridge County , Kentucky . An unincorporated community in Frederick County , Maryland . A township and unincorporated community therein, in Bay County , Michigan . A township and unincorporated community therein, in Grand Traverse County , Michigan . A former post office in Richland Township, Missaukee County , Michigan . An unincorporated community in Swan Creek Township, Saginaw County , Michigan . A minor city in Douglas County , Minnesota , named after the president. An unincorporated community in Oregon County , Missouri , named after the president. A city in Bergen County , New Jersey , renamed after the president. A census-designated place in Doña Ana County , New Mexico . An unincorporated community in Coal Township, Jackson County , Ohio . An unincorporated community in Mahoning County , Ohio . A neighbourhood in the East End of Pittsburgh , Pennsylvania . A census-designated place in Travis County , Texas . A locale in Springfield , Fairfax County , Virginia . A minor city in Whitman County , Washington , named after the president. An unincorporated community in Jackson County , West Virginia . A town in Jackson County , Wisconsin . A town in Polk County , Wisconsin . An unincorporated community in Portage County , Wisconsin . A number of other townships in the United States , listed under Garfield Township .
